Di den cuoi dau hoac cuoi ngoac kep            ctrl + shift + \
Tim kiem o tat ca cac file                     ctrl + shift + f
Reopen a closed file                           ctrl + shift + t
Tim file roi mo no                             ctrl + shift + e  
Them con tro vao cac dong khac                 ctrl + shift + PgUp, ctrl + shift + PgDn
Di chuyen nhanh con tro sang trai hoac phai    ctrl + ->, ctrl + <-
Di chuyen giua cac tab                         Giu Alt roi an cac so tuong ung so thu tu cua tab
Xoa 1 tu o phia truoc                          ctrl + backspace
Duplicate line                                 ctrl + shift + d
Xoa 1 dong                                     ctrl + x
split editor                                   ctrl + \
select word                                    ctrl + d
bat hoac tat slide bar                         ctrl + b
Go to symbols in file                          ctrl + shift + o
Column selection                               Giu shift + alt roi di chuot
Comment cai dong do                            ctrl + /
Close cai tab hien tai                         ctrl + w
Zoom in/out                                    ctrl + =/-
Thay the                                       ctrl + h
Select all occurences of Find match            alt + enter
1 cach tien hon la                             ctrl + shift + l

(O cac ban phim khong co nut home/end thi thay vao do se la fc <- va fn ->)
di chuyen den dau hoac cuoi file               ctrl + fn <- hoac ctrl + fn ->
di chuyen con tro den dau hoac cuoi file       fn <-, fn ->

scroll nhung khong thay doi con tro            ctrl + PgUp, ctrl + PgDn
